NOOP:

Hostmask ya da sunucu bazinca IRCop yetkisi almanizi
engeller. Oper girildiginde eslesen kullaniciya kill atilir.

Sentaks: NOOP ADD HOSTMASK <nick!user@host> [sebep]
Sentaks: NOOP ADD SERVER <mask> [sebep]

Kullanimi:
    /msg &nick& NOOP ADD HOSTMASK *!*@some.spoof Abusive operator
    /msg &nick& NOOP ADD SERVER bad.server Abusive admin

Sentaks: NOOP DEL HOSTMASK <nick!user@host>
Sentaks: NOOP DEL SERVER <mask>

Kullanimi:
    /msg &nick& NOOP DEL HOSTMASK *!some@operator.host
    /msg &nick& NOOP DEL SERVER bad.server

Sentaks: NOOP LIST HOSTMASK
Sentaks: NOOP LIST SERVER
